{
  "verses": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": [
        "Out of the Depths"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Out of the depthsI cry to You, O LORD!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "O Lord, hear my voice; let Your ears be attentive to my plea for mercy."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "If You, O LORD, kept track of iniquities, then who, O Lord, could st and?"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "But with You there is forgiveness, so that You may be feared."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I wait for the LORD; my soul does wait, and in His word I put my hope."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My soul waits for the Lordmore than watchmen wait for the morning—\nmore than watchmen wait for the morning."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "O Israel, put your hope in the LORD, for with the LORD is loving devotion,\nand with Him is redemption in abundance."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "And He will redeem Israelfrom all iniquity."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}